high_descs: walk straight into the kitchen, turn right at the stove and face the counter
pick up the salt shaker
turn to the right and spin around until you face the counter with the toaster on it
open the right, bottom cabinet, and put the salt  in it, close the door
turn left, walk straight, turn right and face the white table
pick up another salt shaker from the white table
turn left and walk until facing the cabinet with the toaster on top
open the right, bottom cabinet, put the salt shaker to the right of the other one there, close the door
anns.task_desc: pick up two salt shakers and put them in a cabinet below the toaster

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter, left of the stove.
Pick up the salt from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter near the toaster.
Place the salt in the lower cabinet.
Turn left and move to the table.
Pick up the salt from the table.
Turn left, move to the counter near the toaster.
Place the salt in the lower cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt containers into the cabinet.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the sink, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the salt shaker that is on the counter to the left of the oven.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the where the toaster is on the counter.
Open the second cabinet door from the left and place the salt shaker inside on the front left edge, then close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the white table.
Pick up the salt shaker off of the table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to where the toaster is on the counter.
Open the second cabinet door from the left and place the salt shaker inside to the right of the salt shaker that is already in there, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers into a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk forward and left to the counter just left of the oven
Pick up the salt shaker from the kitchen counter near the oven
Turn and walk a few feet left then turn back to face the counter
Open the cabinet below the lettuce on the counter and put the salt shaker in it
Turn left and walk up to the square white table
Pick up the salt shaker from the table
Turn right and walk back to the left most kitchen counter
Open the cabinet below the lettuce on the counter and put the salt shaker in it
anns.task_desc: Put the salt shakers in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Go straight to the sink, turn left and go straight to the counter.
Take the salt next to the phone on the counter on the right.
Turn left, go straight, turn right towards the toaster, move backwards while facing the toaster.
Put the salt in the bottom cabinet that is second from the left under the counter.
Turn left, go straight, turn right and go towards the white table.
Take the salt from the table.
Turn right, go back to facing the toaster.
Put the salt in the bottom cabinet that is second from the left under the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt in a cabinet.

high_descs: move forward towards the pavement
pick up the white container
move left towards the cupboard
drop the container in the cupboard  beneath
turn left towards the table
pick up the container
turn left towards the cupboard
place the container in the cupboard
anns.task_desc: place two white containers in the cupboard
